=========================
 LuaExplorador Changelog
=========================

Version 0.5
-----------

r1593 2014-10-06 14:10:33

- Added support for passing commandline arguments via requester. Lua
  variables 'arg[]' and 'argline' are set in the same way as in LuaX.


Version 0.4
-----------

r1341 2013-06-26 17:23:31

- When Lua program has ended (normally, or with error), the debug process
  now waits in a loop for user pressing "Stop Debug", ignoring all other
  commands.
- Added check for sending messages to the debug process. A requester is
  displayed if debug process is NULL.

r1340 2013-06-25 19:47:38

- Finished switching compiler to GCC4.

r1339 2013-06-22 09:33:16

- Implemented breapkopints.
- Reworked display.
- Added autoscroll (with margins) to the currently executed line.
- Added tab support + its configuration via tooltypes.
